➜到沙滩听海逐浪去 泉州版的“踏浪手册”请查收
http://www.sohu.com/a/411358094_746918	12580
<p class="ql-align-justify">持续不退的高温，让傍晚的海滩成为夏日的宠儿。小编精心整理，为您呈现一份泉州版的“踏浪手册”——到沙滩 听海逐浪去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200804/1eb53f641f21414db152d013d149bd0f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 月亮湾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200804/4c1f8a68b86c431da00ad6849cb0e997.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 傍晚带孩子去海边踏浪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/d66d286e7b9b4c27a14855a971116980.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
